      Goggles is an online coop arena shooter for up to four players. You
      can  play as  one of  four different  characters,  namely  Quentin,
      Frank, Tesla or Jerne. Each character comes with a  unique  set  of
      weapons, vehicle and special abilities. Linux and OS  X  builds  of
      Goggles are currently largely untested and should be viewed  as  if
      in Early Access. We will try our very best to iron out all bugs but
      Linux and OS X users should be warned that we're probably  going to
      need your help.
 
      For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/398830/
